{"tid":1224041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文宣）請搞清楚宣傳對象係邊個","createTime":"2019-06-15T01:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T01:59:41.000Z","uid":102270,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c02bc3de561cc15e2f16cd11e7a83aff26476b","tid":1224041,"uid":102270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:35:36.000Z","msg":"長輩圖嘅戰略係好fun<br />\n亦短期內好似confuse到佢哋咁<br />\n但係呢個唔應該係宣傳嘅重點<br />\n<br />\n我哋諗一諗<br />\n今次宣傳嘅最主要目的有四：<br />\n一、將資訊傳開，保持大家喺警覺狀態，同凝         聚大家<br />\n二、令103萬同中游都星期日上街<br />\n三、拎中游同情<br />\n四、幫之後嘅不合作運動打底<br />\n<br />\n但如果個宣傳對象focus咗喺啲中老年人度，<br />\n對我哋未必有利<br />\n令佢哋迷惘一時，未必可以長遠，<br />\nTVB同紙媒講兩句已經會反回失地<br />\n反而令佢哋對我哋更反感<br />\n佢哋深藍太耐，改變佢哋未必最快最有SO<br />\n唔好全副心機擺哂落去<br />\n<br />\n搞清楚FOCUS<br />\n向中游埋手<br />\n而家啲中游係中游，<br />\n只係因為而家未搞到佢哋利益，佢哋唔出聲<br />\n所以我哋要做嘅係<br />\n<br />\n1.要俾佢哋知修咗例，佢哋啲長遠利益就BYE BYE先<br />\n<br />\n2.俾佢知政府真實嘅所作所為幾過分<br />\n<br />\n時間唔多，唔好錯FOCUS<br />\n<br />\n小妹淺見。"},{"pid":"366b6c83853ec7e39372e8c38f69f254912549d3","tid":1224041,"uid":102270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295488d66f32dc9c3d5b3676e1264a12cf13aac7","tid":1224041,"uid":102270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86acc7a33d73f043d54ae8eb7061ea56836e1d46","tid":1224041,"uid":102270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa60eecffa9827b18e67c3334065128013ede0a","tid":1224041,"uid":102270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a845464c80cdd145b7253cb786b87680b764772","tid":1224041,"uid":102270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c